hāraṇe; ","target_quote":"在这些方面：(i) 愿望 (adhikāra), (ii) 祝福 (maṅgala), (iii) 完成 (nipphannna), (iv) 特殊限定 (avadhāraṇa),"},{"unit_id":"14-2534-2-9","unit_key":"331447b6-39bb-4b49-ac10-6206db93a050:14-2534-2-9","line":18,"source_quote":"Anantare ca pādāne, atha saddo pavattati. ","target_quote":"(v) 无间 (anantara),  (vi) 分离(apādāna). (以上即）atha的词义。"},{"unit_id":"14-2543-2-11","unit_key":"331447b6-39bb-4b49-ac10-6206db93a050:14-2543-2-11","line":32,"source_quote":"408,431. Dve dve paṭhama majjhimuttamapurisā. ","target_quote":"$两个人便有了“人称”的称谓。$ 第三人称 (paṭhama-purisa)156（156 \"Paṭhama-purisa\" 字面含义 \"第一人\" 但它指第三人称.），第二人称(majjhima-purisa) 和第一人称 (uttamapurisa)."},{"unit_id":"14-2549-2-12","unit_key":"331447b6-39bb-4b49-ac10-6206db93a050:14-2549-2-12","line":42,"source_quote":"So ca paṭhati, tvañca paṭhasi, tumhe paṭhatha. ","target_quote":"于是他（so)读(paṭhati),你(tvaṃ)读 (paṭhasi); 你们（tumhe)读 (paṭhatha)."},{"unit_id":"14-2549-13-19","unit_key":"331447b6-39bb-4b49-ac10-6206db93a050:14-2549-13-19","line":43,"source_quote":"So ca pacati, tvañca pacasi. ","target_quote":"他(so)煮 (pacati), 你(tvaṃ)煮(pacasi);"}],"confidence":0.75,"review_status":"machine_generated"}
